        "logic": "var calc_output = [];\n\nvar age = parseFloat(age);\nvar afp13 = parseFloat(afpl3);\nvar afp = parseFloat(afp);\nvar dcp = parseFloat(dcp);\nvar gender = parseFloat(gender);\n\nvar score = -10.08 + 0.09*age + 1.67*gender + 2.34*Math.log10(afp) + 0.04*afpl3 + 1.33*Math.log10(dcp); \n\nvar prob = (Math.exp(score) / (1 + Math.exp(score)))*100;\n\n//results\n\ncalc_output.push({\n   name: 'mini',\n   value: prob.toFixed(2),\n   value_text: '%',\n   message:'Probability of concurrent HCC'\n});\ncalc_output.push({\n    name: '10094_GALAD Model for HCC_result (score)',\n    value: score.toFixed(2),\n    value_text: 'points',\n    message: 'GALAD Score'\n});\ncalc_output.push({\n    name: '10094_GALAD Model for HCC_result (risk)',\n    value: prob.toFixed(2),\n    value_text: '%',\n    message: 'Probability of concurrent HCC in this CLD patient'\n});\n\n",
